title: Season 6?
body: Just wondering when it starts, can't find any information on it so far & it's normally around this time, thanks in advance.

replies.body: You didn't look very hard then. Second page on the League News tab, you would have found [this](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/competitive/2016-ranked-season-kicks-soon).

There is a glitch with my masteries for Season 6, it keeps saying an error has occurred and I cannot use masteries. I would be very grateful if this error gets patched immediately. If anyone has any idea's to help me, please let me know.
You wont get much help in the comments for that. I suggest you create a new discussion [here](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous/submit).
